{"timestamp":"2026-06-09T08:34:37.809Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"call_dcctKNH55Wr9P79tUZYyrd55","output":"Chunk ID: cc4b7e\nWall time: 0.4416 seconds\nProcess exited with code 0\nOriginal token count: 2282\nOutput:\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6H-nRa\ttrue\tsrc/server/http/qr-code.web-handler.ts\tnull\t**<sub><sub>![P1 Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/P1-orange?style=flat)</sub></sub>  Restore authorization for registration QR codes**  By ignoring `requestContext` here, the handler now returns a QR image for any confirmed `registrationId` without checking authentication, tenant ownership, the registration owner, or organizer access. In the inspected `/qr/registration/:registrationId` route this means an anonymous or cross-tenant request that knows or obtains a registration id can fetch the ticket QR that was previously restricted to the attendee or organizers.\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3376695363\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6H-nRd\tfalse\tsrc/server/effect/rpc/handlers/events/events-registration.handlers.ts\t1948\t**<sub><sub>![P2 Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/P2-yellow?style=flat)</sub></sub>  Collect required answers before creating transfer replacements**  When a paid transfer code is redeemed for an event whose registration option has required questions, this path inserts the replacement registration directly and the RPC payload only contains `code`/`eventId`, so the normal `validateRegistrationQuestionAnswers` path never runs and no `eventRegistrationQuestionAnswers` rows are inserted. The redeemer can complete checkout with a confirmed registration missing required form data that normal registration would reject; collect answers in the transfer flow or explicitly handle how those answers should transfer.\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3376695366\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IA0RY\tfalse\tsrc/server/effect/rpc/handlers/events/events-registration.handlers.ts\t1851\t**<sub><sub>![P2 Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/P2-yellow?style=flat)</sub></sub>  Allow public options to be redeemed by transfer**  For paid transfer-code redemption on registration options with no role restrictions, `roleIds` is an empty array, which the normal registration path treats as open to everyone via `isUserEligibleForRegistrationOption`. This new check rejects those same public options because `.some(...)` is false for an empty array, so transfer links for ordinary public paid tickets always fail with “User is not eligible”; handle the empty-role case as eligible here too.\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377498054\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IA0Rc\ttrue\tsrc/server/effect/rpc/handlers/events/events-registration.handlers.ts\tnull\t**<sub><sub>![P2 Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/P2-yellow?style=flat)</sub></sub>  Charge transfer replacements from the gross price**  When the source payment has already been reconciled by the `charge.succeeded` webhook, that handler overwrites `transactions.amount` with Stripe's net balance transaction amount, so using `sourcePaidTransaction.amount` as the new Checkout `unit_amount` charges the replacement attendee less than the original gross ticket price and then applies a new application fee on top of the reduced amount. This affects normal paid registrations after Stripe fee reconciliation; preserve/use the original gross amount for the replacement checkout instead of the net accounting amount.\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377498059\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH8T\tfalse\tdrizzle/20260602024500_registration_transfer_intents/migration.sql\t20\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🔴 Critical_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Enforce a single active transfer intent per source registration.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615848\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH8W\tfalse\thelpers/testing/runtime-environment.ts\t40\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟡 Minor_  <details>\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615855\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH8j\tfalse\tsrc/app/admin/role-details/role-details.component.html\t20\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟡 Minor_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Use duotone icon component for the new edit action icon.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615874\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH8p\tfalse\tsrc/app/admin/user-list/user-list.component.spec.ts\t10\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟡 Minor_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Resolve template path relative to the spec file, not `process.cwd()`.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615884\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH89\tfalse\tsrc/app/events/event-edit/event-edit.html\t21\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟡 Minor_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Add `type=\"button\"` to the header menu trigger.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615908\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9D\tfalse\tsrc/app/events/event-organize/event-organize.spec.ts\t59\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟡 Minor_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Use a stable boundary for participant section slicing.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615922\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9S\tfalse\tsrc/server/discounts/discount-provider-config.ts\t42\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_  <details>\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615949\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9W\tfalse\tsrc/server/effect/rpc/handlers/admin.handlers.ts\t142\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Enforce integer checks for registration-limit policy values.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615953\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9X\tfalse\tsrc/server/effect/rpc/handlers/events/events-registration.handlers.spec.ts\t137\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟡 Minor_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Replace `Date.now()`-based fixture times with fixed timestamps.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615954\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9a\tfalse\tsrc/server/effect/rpc/handlers/events/events-registration.handlers.ts\t2009\t_🧹 Nitpick_ | _🔵 Trivial_ | _💤 Low value_  **Consider passing `pinnedNowIso` for e2e test consistency.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615958\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9c\tfalse\tsrc/server/effect/rpc/handlers/finance/finance-receipts.handlers.ts\t709\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Re-check receipt status atomically in the update WHERE clause.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615961\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9f\tfalse\tsrc/server/effect/rpc/handlers/finance/finance.handlers.spec.ts\t236\t_🧹 Nitpick_ | _🔵 Trivial_ | _💤 Low value_  **Consider replacing shift-based mock with explicit call tracking.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615965\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9j\tfalse\tsrc/server/email/email-notification-dispatcher.ts\t103\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Add a timeout/cancellation path for outbound Resend requests.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615970\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9p\tfalse\tsrc/server/email/email-notification-dispatcher.ts\t139\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_ | _🏗️ Heavy lift_  **Add atomic claim semantics before sending outbox rows.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615977\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9s\ttrue\tsrc/server/http/qr-code.web-handler.ts\tnull\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🔴 Critical_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Restore explicit authorization before returning confirmed-registration QR codes.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615979\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9t\tfalse\tsrc/server/http/stripe-webhook.web-handler.ts\t167\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_  <details>\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615981\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH9w\tfalse\tsrc/shared/rpc-contracts/app-rpcs/admin.rpcs.ts\t223\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Constrain registration-limit fields to valid domain values at the RPC boundary.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615988\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH94\tfalse\ttests/docs/events/register.doc.ts\t85\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Add a timeout to the Docker secret probe.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377615999\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH-C\tfalse\ttests/docs/users/create-account.doc.ts\t206\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Scope tenant-user lookup and cleanup to the active tenant.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377616015\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH-E\tfalse\ttests/specs/finance/stripe-webhook-replay.spec.ts\t16\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟡 Minor_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Fail fast when organizer fixture is missing.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377616020\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH-O\ttrue\ttests/specs/profile/create-account.spec.ts\t112\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_ | _⚡ Quick win_  **Restore tenant-scoped lookup for the created tenant user.**\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377616032\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH-R\tfalse\ttests/support/reporters/documentation-reporter/take-screenshot.ts\t33\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_  <details>\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377616036\nPRRT_kwDONgQCms6IBH-V\tfalse\ttests/support/utils/doc-screenshot.ts\t35\t_⚠️ Potential issue_ | _🟠 Major_  <details>\thttps://github.com/evorto-app/app/pull/69#discussion_r3377616041\n"}}
