{"timestamp":"2026-06-09T09:03:24.453Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"thread_goal_updated","threadId":"019ea60b-1a1c-7703-b8d8-26ed57eb7f8e","turnId":"39b34c3d-7618-4472-ab5a-541b5eafa5e4","goal":{"threadId":"019ea60b-1a1c-7703-b8d8-26ed57eb7f8e","objective":"Finalize the stacked split PRs for evorto-app/app#62 from lowest to highest PR number. For each PR #63 through #71, inspect unresolved review comments and failing checks, verify whether downstream stacked PRs already address each issue, make only the minimal necessary fixes, reply to comments when no code change is needed, resolve completed threads, and keep every split PR ready for review with no PR over 150 changed files. \nOnce one PR is done, you can set the next one to ready for review so coderabbit will check. Try to avoid rate limits. Preserve the final stacked code state so the top split branch remains equivalent to the current PR #62 assembly branch.","status":"active","tokensUsed":14889373,"timeUsedSeconds":75505,"createdAt":1780920299,"updatedAt":1780995804}}}
